\n            <div class=\"page-main\">\n                 <div class=\"page-main\">\n                    <div class=\"left-menu\">\n                    <div class=\"head\">\n\n\n\n师资情况</div>\n                   <ul>\n\n       <a href=\"../../szqk/lyys1.htm\" title=\"两院院士\"><li class=\"    \">两院院士</li></a>\n\n       <a href=\"../../szqk/jsdw1.htm\" title=\"教师队伍\"><li class=\"   on   \">教师队伍</li></a>\n\n       <a href=\"../../szqk/gcjsryjzy1.htm\" title=\"工程技术人员及职员\"><li class=\"    \">工程技术人员及职员</li></a>\n\n       <a href=\"../../szqk/txry.htm\" title=\"退休人员\"><li class=\"    \">退休人员</li></a>\n    <div style=\"width:100%;height:25px;\"></div>\n</ul>\n                </div>\n                <div class=\"right-main-box-box\">\n                    <div class=\"right-main-box\">\n                        <div style=\"width:100%;height:43px;\"></div>\n                        <div class=\"right-main\">\n                            <div class=\"right-map\">\n                                <div class=\"left\">\n\n\n\n教师队伍</div>\n                                <div class=\"right\">当前位置：\n                      <a href=\"../../index.htm\" style=\"color: #165068;\">  首页</a>\n                &gt;\n              <a href=\"../../szqk/lyys1.htm\" style=\"color: #165068;\">  师资情况</a>\n                &gt;\n              <a href=\"../../szqk/jsdw1.htm\" style=\"color: #165068;\">  教师队伍</a>\n                &gt;\n                正文\n</div>\n                                </div>\n                             \n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n<script language=\"javascript\" src=\"../../_dwr/interface/NewsvoteDWR.js\"></script><script language=\"javascript\" src=\"../../_dwr/engine.js\"></script><script language=\"javascript\" src=\"/system/resource/js/news/newscontent.js\"></script><link href=\"/system/resource/style/component/news/content/format2.css\" type=\"text/css\" rel=\"stylesheet\"><script language=\"javascript\" src=\"/system/resource/js/ajax.js\"></script><form name=\"_newscontent_fromname\">\n\n<div class=\"szdw-detail right-column-box\">\n<div class=\"basic-box\">\n                                    <div class=\"timg\"><img src=\"/__local/3/92/32/41EFAB937B1B5ACD3D2391A2F97_7494D993_263A.jpg\"></div>\n                                    <div class=\"tbasic\">\n                                        <div class=\"tname\">马　静</div>\n                                        <div class=\"tname-bg\"></div>\n                                        <div class=\"tag\">副教授</div>\n                                        <div class=\"clear\"></div>\n                                        <div class=\"tcontent\" style=\"height: 180px;\">\n                                            <p> \n\n     博士生导师<br>\n     \n     电话：010-62788237<br>\n\n      电子邮箱：<a href=\"mailto:ma-jing at tsinghua.edu.cn\">ma-jing at tsinghua.edu.cn</a><br>\n     \n     办公地址：清华大学逸夫技术科学楼A504<br>\n\n     每年招收1-2名博士生，常年招收博士后<br>\n\n</p>\n                                            \n                                        </div>\n                                       <div class=\"more\" style=\"display: block;\"><span>展开更多&gt;&gt;</span></div>\n                                    </div>\n                                    <div class=\"clear\"></div>\n                                </div>\n<ul class=\"right-column-menu tright-column-menu\">\n                                    <li title=\"title1\" class=\"on\">   \n                                    <div class=\"block\"></div>               \n                                    <div class=\"text\">教育背景</div>         \n                                    <div class=\"block\"></div></li> \n                                    <li title=\"title2\">   \n                                    <div class=\"block\"></div>               \n                                    <div class=\"text\">工作履历</div>         \n                                    <div class=\"block\"></div></li> \n                                    <li title=\"title3\">   \n                                    <div class=\"block\"></div>               \n                                    <div class=\"text\">主要讲授课程</div>         \n                                    <div class=\"block\"></div></li> \n                                    <li title=\"title4\">   \n                                    <div class=\"block\"></div>               \n                                    <div class=\"text\">研究领域</div>         \n                                    <div class=\"block\"></div></li> \n                                    <li title=\"title5\">   \n                                    <div class=\"block\"></div>               \n                                    <div class=\"text\">奖励与荣誉</div>         \n                                    <div class=\"block\"></div></li> \n                                    <li title=\"title6\">   \n                                    <div class=\"block\"></div>               \n                                    <div class=\"text\">学术成果</div>         \n                                    <div class=\"block\"></div></li> \n \n                                    \n                                </ul>\n                                <div class=\"tli-content title1 tli-content-on\">\n                                <div class=\"v_news_content\">\n<p style=\"margin-bottom: 5px;\">2002/09-2006/07 清华大学材料科学与工程系，学士</p>\n<p style=\"margin-bottom: 5px;\">2006/08-2011/07 清华大学材料科学与工程系，博士</p>\n</div>\n                                </div>\n                                <div class=\"tli-content title2 tli-content-\">\n                                <p style=\"margin-bottom: 5px;\">2012/02-2013/08 瑞典斯德哥尔摩大学材料与环境化学系，博士后</p>\n<p style=\"margin-bottom: 5px;\">2013/09-2015/12 清华大学材料学院，讲师</p>\n<p style=\"margin-bottom: 5px;\">2016/01-2019/06 清华大学材料学院，助理教授</p>\n<p style=\"margin-bottom: 5px;\">2019/06-2021/12 清华大学材料学院，准聘副教授</p>\n<p style=\"margin-bottom: 5px;\">2021/12<span style=\"text-indent: 28px;\">-</span>至今 清华大学材料学院，长聘副教授</p>\n                                </div>\n                                <div class=\"tli-content title3 tli-content-\">\n                                <p style=\"margin-bottom: 5px;\">研究生专业课 材料学基础（70350043）</p>\n<p style=\"margin-bottom: 5px;\">研究生学术与职业素养课程 材料学科研究生学术规范与职业伦理（80350651）</p>\n<p style=\"margin-bottom: 5px;\">本科生理工融合课程 材料与物理（44730182）</p>\n                                </div>\n                                <div class=\"tli-content title4 tli-content-\">\n                                <p class=\"vsbcontent_start\">铁电/多铁性材料及原型器件、强关联功能氧化物薄膜</p>\n                                </div>\n                                <div class=\"tli-content title5 tli-content-\">\n                                <p style=\"margin-bottom: 5px;\">2023 中国电介质物理优秀青年奖（A类）</p>\n<p style=\"margin-bottom: 5px;\">2021 高等学校科学研究优秀成果奖（科学技术）自然科学奖一等奖（排名第三）</p>\n<p style=\"margin-bottom: 5px;\">2020 清华大学青年教师教学优秀奖</p>\n<p style=\"margin-bottom: 5px;\">2019 国家自然科学基金委优秀青年科学基金</p>\n<p style=\"margin-bottom: 5px;\">2019 国家高层次人才特殊支持计划青年拔尖人才</p>\n<p style=\"margin-bottom: 5px;\">2015 中国科协青年人才托举工程</p>\n<p style=\"margin-bottom: 5px;\">2013 清华大学“基础研究青年人才计划”</p>\n<p style=\"margin-bottom: 5px;\">2013 全国百篇优秀博士学位论文</p>\n<p style=\"margin-bottom: 5px;\">2012 北京市优秀博士学位论文</p>\n                                </div>\n                                <div class=\"tli-content title6 tli-content-\">\n                                <p class=\"vsbcontent_start\">部分论文列表：</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"color: windowtext; font-family: &quot;times new roman&quot;;\">1． </span><span style=\"color: windowtext; font-family: &quot;times new roman&quot;;\">H. J. Han, J. Ma, J. Wang, E. X. Xu, Z. Q. Xu, H. B. Huang, Y. Shen, C.-W. Nan, </span><b style=\"color: windowtext; font-family: &quot;times new roman&quot;; text-indent: 2em;\">J. Ma</b><sup style=\"color: windowtext; font-family: &quot;times new roman&quot;; text-indent: 2em;\">*</sup><span style=\"color: windo